sheep dip
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:a pot or swim dip in which sheep are washed to eradicate ticks, lice, mites, keds and other agents of infection.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: aka sheep-dip, sheepdip
Citations
